splash.splashContent:
Geodetic Control Network (built for Zimbabwe) 
The GCN application will help you easily find locations, details, and specifications of the Geodetics Control Network in Zimbabwe. 
New User? We recommend using the Help feature   within the app which provides information on how to use the app. 
The application might require your current location (position) for some functionality to produce the best results to enhance your experience. We do not store your location data, once you are done and close this app, that's the end of the tracking session. 

Developed by - Surveyor-Jr
Contact me via Email at: me@surveyor-jr.tech
